    {
      "id": "670827",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "MasonQian",
        "uid": "15361"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t不需要阻止啊<br/>\n不過拼多多的貨確實是很爛<br/>\n淘寶天貓京東堪用的東西挺多的<br/>\n<br/>\n你就算在Amazon甚至Walmart買<br/>\n還是很多淘寶貨啊\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-07-15",
